        <paragraph>Cron script to generate usage notifications for volumes existing during
            the audit period.</paragraph>
        <paragraph>Together with the notifications generated by volumes
            create/delete/resize, over that time period, this allows an external
            system consuming usage notification feeds to calculate volume usage
            for each tenant.</paragraph>
        <paragraph>Time periods are specified as ‘hour’, ‘month’, ‘day’ or ‘year’</paragraph>
        <bullet_list bullet="-">
            <list_item>
                <paragraph><title_reference>hour</title_reference> - previous hour. If run at 9:07am, will generate usage for
                    8-9am.</paragraph>
            </list_item>
            <list_item>
                <paragraph><title_reference>month</title_reference> - previous month. If the script is run April 1, it will
                    generate usages for March 1 through March 31.</paragraph>
            </list_item>
            <list_item>
                <paragraph><title_reference>day</title_reference> -  previous day. if run on July 4th, it generates usages for
                    July 3rd.</paragraph>
            </list_item>
            <list_item>
                <paragraph><title_reference>year</title_reference> - previous year. If run on Jan 1, it generates usages for
                    Jan 1 through Dec 31 of the previous year.</paragraph>
            </list_item>
        </bullet_list>
